WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:07.793
Hey, good morning family. Well, I have a hard word to give, but first off, I want to tell you all thank you for praying for me.

00:00:07.794 --> 00:00:11.867
Thank you for being here and being a part of this family, this prayer channel.

00:00:11.868 --> 00:00:19.138
You know, I was going to do this word yesterday and I was going to tell you what the Lord is showing me concerning America and what's coming.

00:00:19.139 --> 00:00:22.859
But I didn't want to come out and just give it. I wanted to pray over it.

00:00:22.860 --> 00:00:26.094
Yesterday, like I said, I was driving around and the Lord gave me the word.

00:00:26.095 --> 00:00:29.542
He said, 'I want you to go home and I want you to dig in the flower beds.

00:00:29.543 --> 00:00:35.388
I want you to go outside and pull weeds right now.'I said, 'Well, I'm going to go in and do the video.'He said, 'No, you're not.

00:00:35.389 --> 00:00:52.316
You're going to go outside and pull weeds.'I said, 'Yes, sir.'So, I was out there just praying in the spirit and just pulling weeds in the flower bed all afternoon and just praying and asking Him, 'So, what do you want me to say?'And He said, 'Nothing yet.

00:00:52.317 --> 00:00:59.350
Go low. Go slow. Go low inside. Go deep inside. Pray in the spirit and go slow about it.

00:00:59.351 --> 00:01:03.439
Don't be quick to deliver a word. There's no urgency.'And He gave me the scriptures.

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:14.666
He said, 'Ephesians 5:1: Be an imitator of God, as dear children imitate their earthly fathers.

00:01:14.667 --> 00:01:25.112
Imitate the Lord.'And I was like, 'So what do you mean by that?'And He started talking about how He wasn't quick to go out and raise Lazarus from the dead.

00:01:25.113 --> 00:01:28.999
The urgency was there and everybody was pushing Him, saying, 'Lazarus is sick.

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:35.510
He's dying,'and all the things were going around—all the voices around Him.

00:01:35.511 --> 00:01:48.698
He was hearing Lazarus is sick and dying, and all the voices around Him were trying to pressure Him to move out of what God was telling Him to do, which was stay still, peace, peace.

00:01:48.699 --> 00:01:59.994
Four days go by, and Jesus goes, and they said, 'He stinks, Lord.'So there was no urgency in His spirit except to follow what the Father had told Him to do.

00:01:59.995 --> 00:02:12.756
Then He started bringing up Mary and Martha. Mary was sitting at the feet of Jesus, listening to Him, staying vertical. She didn't do what Martha was doing.

00:02:12.757 --> 00:02:25.482
Martha was in there probably throwing pots and pans around, getting all upset because nobody was in there helping her, because she felt it was urgent to cook the food for all the disciples and for Jesus.

00:02:25.483 --> 00:02:31.553
And so Mary is doing what we should be doing, staying at the feet of Jesus.

00:02:31.554 --> 00:02:37.596
There's no urgency when you're in peace like that, is what the Lord was showing me.

00:02:37.597 --> 00:02:46.290
Be an imitator of God. What did Jesus do? He stayed, and He heard the Father's voice concerning Lazarus.

00:02:46.291 --> 00:02:53.508
And what did Mary do? She stayed at His feet. Martha was out there doing all the busy work, but she should have been at the feet, too.

00:02:53.509 --> 00:03:11.155
The urgency of the hour is staying at the feet of Jesus, not being moved by the circumstances of what you're seeing in the news, thinking, 'I've got to come out and tell everybody what the Lord is saying.'And the Lord said, 'No, pull weeds.'I said, 'Whoa, I don't understand.'But it's called dying to self, and it's His channel.

00:03:11.156 --> 00:03:21.439
And that's what He was trying to get across to me: no matter how much you think you need to deliver a word because you know it's important, this is more important.

00:03:21.440 --> 00:03:30.301
'I need you to rest. I need you to stay right here at my feet right now, vertical. There's much that I need to talk to you about.

00:03:30.302 --> 00:03:42.893
And the only way you're going to hear what I'm going to tell you is by staying right here like Mary. Don't be Martha right now, Brandon.

00:03:42.894 --> 00:03:49.913
Stay at my feet.'There are a lot of people being Marthas, and they're running around trying to make the first video and be the first.

00:03:49.914 --> 00:03:56.034
He said, 'But it's more important to be accurate, and the only way you stay accurate is staying at my feet.

00:03:56.035 --> 00:04:05.551
Pull weeds.'And I was like, you know, you have all these things going, 'Well, I've got to pull weeds.

00:04:05.552 --> 00:04:17.940
Be still.'Do you know how hard it is sometimes when you feel like you haven't heard the word and you're going, 'Well, Lord, you gave me the word, so...'But here I was, and I started praying in the spirit, and you know what He started doing?

00:04:17.941 --> 00:04:27.501
He started showing me flowers. I started praying in the spirit and I'm looking and seeing if He's going to show me anything else, and He started showing me flowers.

00:04:27.502 --> 00:04:37.218
I saw beautiful lavender flowers that looked like heaven. It was glimpses, and I started weeping because of the beauty of the flowers.

00:04:37.219 --> 00:04:40.018
And He said, 'Remember, just like George Washington Carver, Brandon.

00:04:40.019 --> 00:04:55.110
He was the man that talked with the flowers, and God showed him the secret things because he put God first, and he didn't let the clutter cloud his mind of what was going on around him.

00:04:55.111 --> 00:04:59.685
He took time to spend with the Great Creator every single day at four o'clock in the morning.

00:04:59.686 --> 00:05:09.581
And no matter how much was going around him, he would always talk to the peanut, and the peanut shared its secrets with him.'George Washington Carver was a great man of God.

00:05:09.582 --> 00:05:24.052
And so I want to tell you, for what I'm about to tell you, this came later—more of what He was showing me is in store: 'A great shaking to awaken.'He keeps talking to me about it.

00:05:24.053 --> 00:05:36.036
And at this time, I was so tired. I was dozing off, and all of a sudden He wanted to talk more about what's coming, and I had heavy eyes.

00:05:36.037 --> 00:05:44.554
I was on the couch, and I was bobbing, doing the old bob. All of a sudden, He said, 'I have something to say.'And I went, 'Yes, sir.

00:05:44.555 --> 00:05:50.031
What's going on?'You know, and I started praying, and I'm talking down low.

00:05:50.032 --> 00:05:56.863
I said, 'Well, Lord, you picked a real fine time.'But it's not in my time; it's in Yours. It was when my flesh was out of the way.

00:05:56.864 --> 00:06:13.971
I was completely exhausted, and I told my son, 'Grab the recorder.'I said, 'The Father's going to talk, and I'm really tired right now, but I'm going to say what He says.'But I was dead to my flesh at that point instead of being like a chicken with its head cut off, flapping its wings all around.

00:06:13.972 --> 00:06:18.638
It was at the time when my flesh was out of the way and He could talk the loudest.

00:06:18.639 --> 00:06:26.879
And I said, 'You know, Lord, You really are so amazing to me.''Focus on the flowers today, Brandon.

00:06:26.880 --> 00:06:34.236
Focus on the flowers.'And there will be a lot of you who say, 'Oh, Brandon, get to it.'I just did. I just did.

00:06:34.237 --> 00:06:41.551
I just told you a vital piece of the puzzle that many of you will try to bypass because you're so busy.

00:06:41.552 --> 00:06:47.960
But like the Lord is always telling me, He said, 'You're in a hurry to go nowhere. Nothing else matters.

00:06:47.961 --> 00:07:00.399
Everything that you're trying to achieve on this earth is going to be gone.'Most people are trying to build their future and all these great things, the wealth and all the things on this earth.

00:07:00.400 --> 00:07:07.986
But the Lord said to me, 'Brandon, sow the seeds for the thousand years. Sow the seeds for what you'll reap on the other side.

00:07:07.987 --> 00:07:12.113
For what you sow in secret, you'll be rewarded openly.'So, this is what I saw.

00:07:12.114 --> 00:07:15.864
You know, a lot of people are focused on the peace agreement.

00:07:15.865 --> 00:07:28.879
They're saying, 'Hey, we're going to have a ceasefire and all these things.'And if you go back to the video where I was praying—I gave a short on it back in December—the Lord showed me that they'll call peace and safety.

00:07:28.880 --> 00:07:37.631
