00:07:37.632 --> 00:07:46.478
Seven months later, and He's warning about sudden destruction, major attacks still coming.

00:07:46.479 --> 00:07:55.590
They are not satisfied with what they have achieved. Iran is saying this because they lost so much.

00:07:55.591 --> 00:08:03.291
